<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">والجميع:</span> خور.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">ونخلة خوارة:</span> صفيٌّ كثيرة الحمل.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
